      "Description": "The Contract is amended by adding the following: Verification of Vaccines. In compliance with the State and Indiana State Psychiatric Hospital Personnel policies, verification of all vaccines, including annual flu vaccination, is required for all healthcare/contracted personnel who have job duties or physical presence inside any Indiana State Psychiatric Hospital in the course of conducting their work. This policy applies to all personnel which includes State employees, medical staff, pharmacy staff, clinical staff, volunteers, students, and specified vendors at all Indiana State Psychiatric Hospitals."
